        </div>
        <div className={styles.programDetails}>
          <div className={styles.dot1}>&nbsp;</div>
          <div className={styles.text1}>
            {`You can redeem upto ${isUS ? 1 : 30} Credits for each order. (For eg: If your logistics amount is
